Product description

This officially licensed Coca-Cola wall mirror is the perfect gift for the Coca-Cola lover in your life. Features include: Black wood frames. Mirror with print. Big 15 x 26 inch Overall Size. Great for gifts and recreation decor.

From the manufacturer

Mirror Assembly Process

Frame Construction

Frames cut and joined in house to order.

Frame Construction Continued

Full constructed frame.

Wide Format Printing

Reverse printed artwork to protect the print behind glass.

Read more

Mirror Prep

Mirrored glass is wiped clean.

Mirror Prep Continued

Printed glass cleaned and placed on top of mirrored glass.

Framing Process

Frame applied to glass layers.

Read more

Cardboard Backing

Cardboard backing applied to framed glass.

Final Installation

All materials securely fastened to the frame.

Hanging Hardware Included

Scissor Hook pre-insatlled for hanging mirror.

Read more

Frame Re-inforcement

Gussets installed on each corner to re-inforce the frame structure.

Finished Mirror

Finished mirror ready for hanging.

Made in the USA

Built with pride in the USA!

How are ratings calculated?
To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzes reviews to verify trustworthiness.
